{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[mow]]; to [[cut]]; to [[weed]]
#* {{zh-x|葛 之 覃 兮、施 于 中-谷。<br>維 葉 莫-莫、是 刈 是 濩。<br>為 絺 為 綌、服 之 無斁{yì}。|How the dolichos spread itself out, extending to the middle of the valley!<br> Its leaves were luxuriant and dense. I '''cut''' it and I boiled it,<br> And made both fine cloth and coarse, which I will wear without getting tired of it.|ref=Shijing}}
# {{lb|zh|obsolete}} [[crop]]s that have been [[cut]]
#* {{zh-x|一 春 違 其 農，二 夏 食 其 穀，三 秋 取 其 刈，四 冬 凍 其 葆。|First, in spring encircle their farmlands; second, in summer eat their provisions; third, in autumn seize their '''harvests / crops''', in winter expose their stores.|ref=Yizhoushu}}
# {{lb|zh|literary}} [[sickle]]
#* {{zh-x|時雨 既 至，挾 其 槍、刈、耨、鎛，以 旦-暮 從事 於 田野。|When the timely seasonal rain is just come, [they farmers] clasp their stakes, '''sickles''', weeders, and hoes to work from dawn to dusk in the fields.|ref=Guoyu}}
